2017-05-27 13-00-00:
	Title: Release 20170527 hotfix now available!
	Author: Paul Chote
	Content: We are today pushing a new bugfix release that addresses a collection of issues that were not found during the playtesting of release-20170421.\n\nThe main changes in this hotfix are:\n • Disabled HiDPI support on Windows, fixing the\n   graphical glitches this caused on non-HiDPI displays.\n • Fixed cursor glitches with the Mono 5 runtime.\n • Fixed the Fullscreen (Legacy) mode on macOS.\n • Several smaller graphical and performance fixes.\n\nHead on over to our www.openra.net to grab the new release, and spread the word!
